data.description: Seller is now offering $3,000 toward buyers closing costs! 3 bed, 2 bath and a large living area! The Kitchen is equipped with ample cabinet and counter space. The beautiful covered patio overlooks the large backyard. Mature trees provide tons of shade and a work shop complete with electricity and an extra storage building! Alley access in the backyard and extra parking in the front! Situated on a quiet cul-de-sac in a convenient location. Near shopping, schools, parks and more!
